def feature(text: str) -> float:
    "Ratio of the longest word length to the total length of the text"
    words = text.split()
    if not words:
        return 0.0
    longest_word_length = max(len(word) for word in words)
    return float(longest_word_length) / len(text) if len(text) > 0 else 0.0

def feature(text: str) -> float:
    "Average length of sentences in characters"
    sentences = re.split(r'[.!?]', text)
    char_count = sum(len(sentence) for sentence in sentences if sentence.strip())
    return float(char_count) / (len(sentences) + 1) if sentences else 0.0

def feature(text: str) -> float:
    "Ratio of non-alphanumeric characters to total characters"
    non_alnum_count = sum(1 for char in text if not char.isalnum())
    return non_alnum_count / len(text) if len(text) > 0 else 0.0

def feature(text: str) -> float:
    "Proportion of non-alphanumeric characters"

    if total_length == 0:

    vowel_count = sum(1 for c in text if c.lower() in 'aeiou')

    return float(vowel_count) / total_chars if total_chars else 0.0

    sentence_count = text.count('.') + text.count('!') + text.count('?')
    total_sentences = len(re.findall(r'[.!?]', text))
    return float(sentence_count) / total_sentences if total_sentences else 0.0
